body_html:
amanbeniwal,

It seems your issue relates to https protocal, can you make some debgging work in you environment, and if confirm it's a issue in tensorflow, and then report it as another new bug here? This bug's root cause is located to the wrong downloading URL in tensorflow source tree, and they already fixed it, and it's closed.
And it seems your issue relates to the SSL&HTTPS, it should be a new issue with another root cause.

Thanks!

Clock
